text: Abdul Kayium (born 17 October 1998) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Twenty20 Cricket League on 25 February 2019. He made his List A debut for Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Cricket League on 8 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
